functions.cpp and functions.h have the test functions.

lbfgs_c.cpp and lbfgs_f.f have the LBFGS solvers in cpp and f90. lbfgs.h is the header file.

nlcg.cpp is nonlinear conjugate gradient

newton.cpp is newton

steepest.cpp is steepest descent

la.cpp has the linear algebra routines.

lsearch.cpp has the line search routines.

test1c.cpp and test1f.cpp are two sample main programs.

See makefile for compilation and run.sh for sample run command
